name: Eleanor Thompson
text: The non-smoking area is small 😖. Other than that it's a nice place to unwind and enjoy yourself.  They no longer give you free play for your birthday. 😖 Some nights they have live music.

name: stephen warren
text: Love the hotel and casino. BBQ restaurant and cafe in back has the worst staff I've ever seen. This is coming from someone who has managed multiple restaurant kitchens. Hit the reset and start fresh with the whole staff.
